### Create sale-linked customer capture session
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sales/{{saleId}}/customer-capture-sessions
X-Staff-Role: STAFF
X-Staff-Id: sale-customer-capture-request
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Get public customer capture session state
GET http://localhost:3000/api/public/customer-capture/{{token}}

### Submit public customer capture details
POST http://localhost:3000/api/public/customer-capture/{{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jamie",
  "lastName": "Rider",
  "email": "jamie.rider@example.com",
  "phone": "07123456789",
  "emailMarketingConsent": true,
  "smsMarketingConsent": false
}
